WEBVTT

00:02.094 --> 00:04.294
Last season on The O.C.:
Theresa's pregnant.

00:04.414 --> 00:06.054
- You don't have to leave.
- Then come with me.

00:06.134 --> 00:08.494
I'm leaving. Can't let Theresa do this by herself.

00:08.534 --> 00:10.054
Oh, my God. It's a palace!

00:10.214 --> 00:12.693
Look, you're getting what you wanted
I'm moving in with you.

00:12.854 --> 00:14.934
- Going somewhere?
- Like, say, San Quentin.

00:14.974 --> 00:17.054
- Thank you.
- Could we convince you to stay?

00:17.214 --> 00:20.174
He's the first real friend I've ever had.
The only real friend I've ever had.

00:20.294 --> 00:23.494
I understand why you have to do this,
but I wish you didn't have to.

00:23.734 --> 00:27.054
Before he got here, I was the biggest loser.
This place was hell for me.

00:27.134 --> 00:30.494
I can't even imagine what it's going
to be like here without him.

